  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, W-EP-04)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package targets Model Risk Level 3 following a revised consequence classification. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed and meet required levels. The 'Equivalency of input parameters' factor is recorded as not-assessed on the grounds that the team judged it inapplicable to a purely computational sensitivity study; however, the correct encoding for that determination would be factorStatus 'not-applicable', not 'not-assessed'. At MRL 3 this omission materially weakens credibility (W-EP-04).",
