    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed and meet or exceed required levels at MRL 3. The equivalency of input parameters factor was judged by the team to be inapplicable and was therefore left not-assessed. The overall credibility evidence is considered sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision that the CFD model adequately identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
